# Ashirwad Sanitary & Tiles - Operating System Terminal Hub

Production full-stack ERP framework constructed natively inside an optimized decoupled Node.js/Express architecture, featuring client token authentication handling, analytical dashboard vectors tracking, and live point-of-sale invoice printing capabilities.

## Production Initialization Sequence Playbook

### 1. Prerequisites Setup
Verify that your operating server node has the latest LTS version of **Node.js (v18+)** along with a live **PostgreSQL (14+)** enterprise instance running safely.

### 2. Local File Cloning
Drop the compiled system blueprint files down structurally into a single project directory mapping folder module context:
```bash
ashirwad-erp/
├── package.json
├── .env.example
├── database.sql
├── server.js
├── index.html
├── style.css
├── script.js
├── manifest.json
└── service-worker.js
